  "body": "### Description\n\nThe kubernetes configuration properties: _quarkus.kubernetes.resources.limits.cpu_, _quarkus.kubernetes.resources.limits.memory_, _quarkus.kubernetes.resources.requests.cpu_, _quarkus.kubernetes.resources.requests.memory_ are compile time properties. \r\nI have different environments where I deploy my service, each environment has a different configuration in terms of available cpus and memory. I would like to define different limits for my service, based on the environment where the service is deployed, without having to recompile it.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nMake the kubernetes limits and requests properties runtime modifiable.",
